reviewText: Love it. Came in 4 days. Watched it the night it arrived. Not just a Christmas special. There are extra clips from other shows at the end.
cute show soon to be a collectors item great service from Amazon as always somehow it's expected now keep up the good work Amazon

Hilarious. Love them. But i bought this thru my friend's account and it came to me with the case damaged in two places, one of them being the circle that holds your dvd in place. So it's obvious something happened and also the dvd was skipping.  Only have watched once so hopefully it doesn't do it anymore since I paid a lot of money for this dvd to add to my Honey Boo Boo collection.
This is/was the best viewing  of Here Comes  Honey Boo Boo.
Where do they get off charging $25 for one episode??? Maybe if they had all the holiday episodes on one DVD, but this is just greed. Would not purchase!
